          "The 'best entrepreneur' profile DECA rewards is a <strong>risk-taker with a strong work ethic</strong> (and self-confidence) who is willing to work far beyond 9-to-5. Personality-trait questions consistently point to risk tolerance + work ethic, not credentials or guaranteed safety.",
          "Entrepreneurs supplement their own expertise with <strong>external resources</strong> — accountants, lawyers, consultants, mentors — rather than trying to do everything alone. DECA tests recognizing when to bring in outside help."
